h care researchers will also analyze changes in variance at adult death and the age distribution of deaths within counties as well as among them in addition they will assemble a uk mortality data set at the local area level and analyze change in the age distribution of deaths within and among local areas this pilot will help illuminate the nature of inequalities in mortality within and between the us and uk especially the puzzling differences that have been reported in the literature this pilot will also prepare us for future international comparisons of the nature and source of mortality inequality within and between countries contact nomita divi search chp search within everything courses events fellowships news op eds people publications research other pages support map & directions contact rss+ rss xml feeds freeman spogli institute for international studies encina hall 616 serra st stanford ca 94305 6055 tel 650 736 0815 fax 650 725 2592 mail code 6055
